{"tid":2248892,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭月娥：這些年來曾經有「出面人招手」希望我「跳槽」，但我仍然堅持做公務、服務市民","createTime":"2020-10-19T03:07:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-19T12:05:11.000Z","uid":212626,"like":9,"dislike":334,"uniUserReply":131,"replies":[{"pid":"9a7c1e7404dd3c86678fc51ac45b1d127d42f2df","tid":2248892,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T03:07:21.000Z","msg":"林鄭月娥在專訪中又提到，自己從事公僕生涯40年，無懼任何打擊，所做的都是為香港好、國家好，問心無愧，會繼續做。她透露這些年來曾經有「出面人招手」希望她「跳槽」，但她仍然堅持做公務、服務市民。<br />\n<br />\n至於過去曾希望增加與立法會議員溝通，每個月到立法會進行「短問短答」環節，但近年行政、立法關係趨緊張，林鄭月娥說如果每次出席只是製造矛盾，看不到有空間交代工作或聽取意見，就去少一些。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1555479-20201019.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1555479-20201019.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=89HDPkshzIuckIexGTa1a0VeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=dbc2d52c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1555479-20201019.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=c80cab02\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1555479-20201019.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6ad42ca16d0e020939b225eff4be1efe6c95abf","tid":2248892,"uid":376274,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T03:07:44.000Z","msg":"Hi"},{"pid":"b13eab2843382c95a70c84418773956f29153cd7","tid":2248892,"uid":359626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T03:07:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"110cea22da193b639b1a09b41ab4c6ddcdfaa80d","tid":2248892,"uid":200343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T03:07:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4652b07477a517143dae8d89d5ad30bc01a6276f","tid":2